       <div>
              
              <p>Popularly known as the best makeup artist in Bangalore, Mangla is the founder of the famous makeup school, Society for International Beauty and Hair Society (SIBHS). SIBHS now functions as a renowned and celebrated beauty and makeup studio in Bangalore.
              <br><br>
              In the recent past, SIBHS has been fortunate to partner with Mrs. India International - Bangalore, where Mangla and her team of experts had provided the contestant with breath-taking makeovers.
              <br><br>
