              <br><br>
              Banasude has also received international certifications in skin care and makeup, from prominent institutions. She was trained under the expertise and guidance of Christine Valmy (USA), Manara Berezina (Gold medallist in Russia) and a few reputed makeup artists of Bollywood.
              <br><br>
              Mangla has had the privilege of working with eminent actors of the film industry, including Mannara Chopra (Priyanka Chopra's cousin), Kannada movie actors Prema and Shubha Poonja and Tamil movie actor Priya Mani.
              <br><br>
              Apart from being a skilled bridal and celebrity makeup artist, Mangla has worked for the fashion, film and television fraternities, and has also been instrumental in enhancing the beauty and looks of models and contestants of various beauty pageants.
